1
00:00:54,119 --> 00:00:55,079
[Killing intent!]

2
00:00:55,079 --> 00:00:55,719
[No!]

3
00:01:11,359 --> 00:01:12,760
Your demon power is weak.

4
00:01:12,920 --> 00:01:14,280
Why bother resisting?

5
00:01:14,760 --> 00:01:17,079
Today, you'll die!

6
00:01:34,760 --> 00:01:36,200
[A'Li.]

7
00:01:36,760 --> 00:01:37,200
[What's wrong?]

8
00:01:37,200 --> 00:01:38,319
[I found a story]

9
00:01:38,319 --> 00:01:39,439
[I must tell you.]

10
00:01:39,560 --> 00:01:40,640
A'Li.

11
00:01:40,760 --> 00:01:42,120
A'Li, something's wrong!

12
00:01:42,239 --> 00:01:44,200
A butterfly flew back from Little White.

13
00:01:44,200 --> 00:01:46,040
He might be caught by a demon hunter!

14
00:01:46,239 --> 00:01:47,439
Stay calm.

15
00:01:47,439 --> 00:01:48,239
I'll be right back.

16
00:01:48,359 --> 00:01:48,959
Okay.

17
00:02:09,799 --> 00:02:11,560
Why hasn't A'Li come back yet?

18
00:02:23,120 --> 00:02:24,039
What are you doing here?

19
00:02:28,520 --> 00:02:29,439
Little Bell Spirit,

20
00:02:30,960 --> 00:02:33,439
have you never left the Demon Village?

21
00:02:34,000 --> 00:02:35,000
So what?

22
00:02:35,439 --> 00:02:37,120
[The guardian of the barrier]

23
00:02:37,599 --> 00:02:39,120
[must not leave the Demon Village.]

24
00:02:39,479 --> 00:02:40,840
[Hidden places]

25
00:02:40,919 --> 00:02:43,520
there will be lion-like Suanni patterns.

26
00:02:44,199 --> 00:02:45,879
It seems my investigation is correct.

27
00:02:46,560 --> 00:02:47,240
You

28
00:02:48,439 --> 00:02:51,560
are the evil spirit guarding the barrier.

29
00:02:52,960 --> 00:02:53,719
Shen Que,

30
00:02:54,080 --> 00:02:55,759
the demons of the Demon Village have never done evil.

31
00:02:56,039 --> 00:02:56,919
If you hurt me,

32
00:02:56,919 --> 00:02:58,039
they will be threatened.

33
00:02:58,039 --> 00:02:59,520
I will definitely take your life.

34
00:02:59,759 --> 00:03:00,840
You will surely regret it.

35
00:03:00,840 --> 00:03:02,400
To slay demons and evil,

36
00:03:02,400 --> 00:03:03,560
what is there to regret?

37
00:03:04,560 --> 00:03:05,719
Focus your mind,

38
00:03:05,719 --> 00:03:06,759
calm the waters...

39
00:04:38,639 --> 00:04:40,000
A'Li!

40
00:04:44,160 --> 00:04:44,720
Zhongjing,

41
00:06:23,079 --> 00:06:24,319
protect His Highness!

42
00:08:14,439 --> 00:08:15,279
A'Li!

43
00:08:15,639 --> 00:08:17,120
You're finally back!

44
00:08:17,120 --> 00:08:18,439
You're finally back!

45
00:08:18,519 --> 00:08:20,240
You know, I've been so worried

46
00:08:20,279 --> 00:08:22,040
that I couldn't eat or sleep!

47
00:08:22,120 --> 00:08:23,199
I had to transform

48
00:08:23,199 --> 00:08:24,519
and force myself to stay calm!

49
00:08:24,560 --> 00:08:25,879
Don't worry.

50
00:08:30,759 --> 00:08:31,560
Little White,

51
00:08:31,879 --> 00:08:33,199
we have to trust A'Li.

52
00:08:33,360 --> 00:08:34,879
She'll handle this.

53
00:08:45,039 --> 00:08:47,200
Love is against selfishness,

54
00:08:47,200 --> 00:08:48,080
cowardice,

55
00:08:48,080 --> 00:08:49,559
betrayal, and greed in one's bones.

56
00:08:49,759 --> 00:08:51,519
Love is a moment outside of order,

57
00:08:52,159 --> 00:08:53,679
knowing the other's shortcomings,

58
00:08:53,720 --> 00:08:55,000
yet always feeling indebted.

59
00:09:08,559 --> 00:09:09,399
A'Li,

60
00:09:09,679 --> 00:09:12,080
recently, you've been entering dreams and getting hurt,

61
00:09:12,080 --> 00:09:13,519
Your spiritual power is greatly depleted.

62
00:09:13,519 --> 00:09:15,720
If you don't consume the nightmares of the Utmost Evil One

63
00:09:15,720 --> 00:09:16,879
and continue cultivation,

64
00:09:17,080 --> 00:09:17,679
I'm afraid

65
00:09:17,679 --> 00:09:19,759
you won't have the strength to keep searching for the Spiritual Root.

66
00:10:12,519 --> 00:10:14,799
I won't forgive you.

67
00:10:15,720 --> 00:10:16,840
Shen Que.

68
00:10:30,840 --> 00:10:32,080
Welcome back, Your Highness.

69
00:10:44,679 --> 00:10:46,039
What are these two baskets?

70
00:10:46,639 --> 00:10:47,360
Your Highness,

71
00:10:47,799 --> 00:10:49,159
this is what Meng Li...

72
00:10:49,159 --> 00:10:50,559
Your Highness, you've had a long day.

73
00:10:50,600 --> 00:10:51,879
Master is still recovering.

74
00:10:52,000 --> 00:10:53,159
He can't meet you for now.

75
00:10:53,360 --> 00:10:54,799
He asked me to tell you,

76
00:10:55,200 --> 00:10:56,799
your bravery in the Demon Village

77
00:10:56,799 --> 00:10:57,679
is commendable.

78
00:10:58,080 --> 00:10:59,279
Your courage is unmatched,

79
00:10:59,279 --> 00:11:00,519
a blessing to the people.

80
00:11:01,000 --> 00:11:02,159
Thank you, State Preceptor.

81
00:11:03,279 --> 00:11:05,080
I'll visit you another day.

82
00:11:05,200 --> 00:11:05,919
Your Highness,

83
00:11:05,919 --> 00:11:06,759
take a good rest.

84
00:11:12,840 --> 00:11:14,360
His Highness was injured by the witch

85
00:11:14,519 --> 00:11:15,679
and lost his memory.

86
00:11:16,080 --> 00:11:18,399
He barely escaped from the Demon Village.

87
00:11:18,960 --> 00:11:19,759
Remember,

88
00:11:19,919 --> 00:11:21,240
don't mention

89
00:11:21,240 --> 00:11:22,639
his past with that witch.

90
00:11:23,080 --> 00:11:24,879
It will confuse him.

91
00:11:25,000 --> 00:11:25,879
That Meng Li

92
00:11:25,879 --> 00:11:27,120
really hurt His Highness?

93
00:11:27,279 --> 00:11:28,399
Don't ask too much.

94
00:11:29,080 --> 00:11:30,159
Just take care of him.

95
00:11:30,399 --> 00:11:30,879
Yes.

96
00:12:40,399 --> 00:12:42,399
Why are you so lazy?

97
00:12:42,759 --> 00:12:45,080
You could have taken shape if you tried harder.

98
00:12:45,600 --> 00:12:47,159
Stop lying there.

99
00:12:47,360 --> 00:12:48,519
Get up and move.

100
00:12:48,840 --> 00:12:49,559
Move.

101
00:12:49,960 --> 00:12:51,600
So what if we take shape?

102
00:12:51,600 --> 00:12:53,320
We just bask in the sun,

103
00:12:53,320 --> 00:12:54,720
absorbing the essence of nature.

104
00:12:54,799 --> 00:12:56,799
Taking shape has many benefits.

105
00:12:56,879 --> 00:12:58,080
You can move freely,

106
00:12:58,200 --> 00:13:00,240
explore every corner of the world,

107
00:13:00,799 --> 00:13:02,240
instead of being stuck in one place

108
00:13:02,240 --> 00:13:04,240
like you are now.

109
00:13:04,519 --> 00:13:06,879
But you've taken human form,

110
00:13:06,879 --> 00:13:08,240
and you're still stuck here.

111
00:13:08,240 --> 00:13:09,600
What's the difference between us?

112
00:13:09,600 --> 00:13:10,039
You...

113
00:13:11,440 --> 00:13:12,519
Alright, Little Bell.

114
00:13:12,519 --> 00:13:13,360
I'm sorry.

115
00:13:13,360 --> 00:13:14,879
I'll cultivate harder.

116
00:13:21,159 --> 00:13:22,080
Don't be upset.

117
00:13:22,320 --> 00:13:23,279
We all know

118
00:13:23,279 --> 00:13:24,960
you stay here to protect

119
00:13:24,960 --> 00:13:26,120
our clan's barrier.

120
00:13:26,720 --> 00:13:28,399
You're a hero to us.

121
00:13:30,559 --> 00:13:32,480
It's good enough.

122
00:13:33,120 --> 00:13:34,600
Our clan is full of

123
00:13:34,600 --> 00:13:35,639
beautiful scenery.

124
00:13:36,200 --> 00:13:38,000
I'm already grateful to

125
00:13:38,000 --> 00:13:39,399
protect such a beautiful place.

126
00:13:39,720 --> 00:13:42,799
But what's the world outside like?

127
00:13:44,159 --> 00:13:45,639
If there were no demon hunters,

128
00:13:45,639 --> 00:13:46,679
I'd like to be the wind,

129
00:13:47,200 --> 00:13:49,159
going wherever I want,

130
00:13:49,639 --> 00:13:51,799
seeing everything in the world.

131
00:13:57,879 --> 00:13:59,000
You never got to see the world

132
00:14:01,000 --> 00:14:03,240
for the sake of our clan.

133
00:14:03,879 --> 00:14:04,720
In your next life,

134
00:14:05,360 --> 00:14:06,399
you can be a tree,

135
00:14:06,799 --> 00:14:07,759
or a gust of wind,

136
00:14:09,720 --> 00:14:10,679
whatever you wish.
